metadata.name: NAZAR BATTU #4 - BOOMBATTU
metadata.description:
The fiercest of them all, Boombattu and her big buns (no puns intended) are constantly at work, recording each and every movement around you. As soon as she detects any evil energy, her deadly buns automatically get activated, shooting high accuracy missiles at the speed of 15,000 mph toward its target. In just 0.02 seconds, your enemy vanishes in a puff of smoke.

STATS 
Weapon - Deadly Buns, Hit-to-Kill Missiles
Defense - 80%
Attack - 95%
Strength - 90%
